{
  "total_duration": 735.315,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 14.104,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Am I all right?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“我是否痊愈？”这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "all right"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是“好吧”，而是 am I okay, am I medically fine。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 14.454,
      "end": 24.694,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课不是医学知识课，也不是教人套医生的话。它是一个 old hospital phone comedy，一个旧式医院电话时代的小反转。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 25.043,
      "end": 40.267,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "John Gilbert 住院以后，想知道自己的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "operation"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "有没有成功。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "operation"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里是 surgery，手术，不是 computer operation，也不是 business operation。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 40.617,
      "end": 48.953,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他直接问医生："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Was my operation successful?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可是医生 refused to tell him，拒绝告诉他。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 49.303,
      "end": 61.262,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二天，他要了一部"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "bedside telephone"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，也就是 hospital bed 旁边的电话。那个年代没有今天这样的 mobile phone, hospital app, or online record。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 61.612,
      "end": 73.924,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他打给"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the hospital exchange"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "exchange"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是交换东西，也不是换钱，而是医院电话总机，负责把电话接到医生那里。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 74.274,
      "end": 83.114,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天医院更重视 privacy。医生通常要确认 identity and authorization，不能随便把病人的手术情况告诉电话里的人。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 83.464,
      "end": 94.984,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以这课的笑点不是“学会骗医生”，而是 old phone system 里发生了一个 misunderstanding：caller 看起来像在问别人，其实他就是 patient 本人。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 95.334,
      "end": 112.534,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "整课记忆链是：doctor refuses -> bedside telephone -> hospital exchange -> Doctor Millington -> certain patient -> operation successful -> allowed to go home -> two more weeks -> relative? -> I am John Gilbert。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 112.884,
      "end": 129.771,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "另外，源数据里英文 hosptial 是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "hospital"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的拼写错误，中文“手术中否成功”按“手术是否成功”理解。我们不改共享数据，但朗读和讲解都按正确意思走。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 130.121,
      "end": 136.561,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一幅画，是 direct question refused。John Gilbert is in hospital，他想知道手术结果。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 136.911,
      "end": 145.167,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文开头说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "While John Gilbert was in hospital, he asked his doctor to tell him whether his operation had been successful."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 145.517,
      "end": 155.421,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里已经不是直接问句了，而是 reported question："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "whether his operation had been successful"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，意思是“他的手术是否已经成功”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 155.771,
      "end": 165.394,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可是后半句来了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "but the doctor refused to do so."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "refused to do so"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是 refused to tell him，医生拒绝告诉他。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 165.744,
      "end": 173.124,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以第一幅画的情绪是 anxious and blocked：John 很想知道答案，但 face to face 的直接路线被关上了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 173.474,
      "end": 182.162,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二幅画，是 another route。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The following day, the patient asked for a bedside telephone."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 182.512,
      "end": 190.904,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The following day"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是 the next day。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "asked for"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里是 requested，要了一部电话。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 191.254,
      "end": 198.049,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "接着："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "When he was alone, he telephoned the hospital exchange and asked for Doctor Millington."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 198.399,
      "end": 209.959,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "alone"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是房里只有他一个人。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "hospital exchange"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是医院总机，operator or switchboard 会把电话接到医生那里。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 210.309,
      "end": 221.309,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "画面可以记成一条 call path：John in bed -> hospital exchange -> Doctor Millington。直接问不行，他换成电话里的 formal route。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 221.659,
      "end": 228.739,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三幅画，是 a formal inquiry。医生接电话以后，John 没有说 “I am John.” 他开始装得很正式。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 229.089,
      "end": 237.445,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "When the doctor answered the phone, Mr. Gilbert said he was inquiring about a certain patient, a Mr. John Gilbert."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 237.794,
      "end": 249.234,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "inquire about"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 ask for information about something，比较正式。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a certain patient"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是某一位病人，也带一点故意神秘的感觉。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 249.584,
      "end": 260.488,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他问："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "if Mr. Gilbert's operation had been successful"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。医生以为这个 caller 是别人，就告诉他："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "it had been"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，手术成功了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 260.838,
      "end": 271.358,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里的 grammar 跟 trick 合在一起：他不是直接问 “Was my operation successful?” 而是间接问 “if Mr. Gilbert's operation had been successful.”"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 271.708,
      "end": 278.755,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四幅画，是 the reveal。John 又问："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "when Mr. Gilbert would be allowed to go home"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 279.105,
      "end": 291.313,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "be allowed to"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 have permission to，被允许做某事。医生告诉他，他还得在医院再待"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "another two weeks"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，也就是 two more weeks。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 291.663,
      "end": 298.439,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后医生问了关键问题："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Dr. Millington asked the caller if he was a relative of the patient."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 298.789,
      "end": 308.26,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "caller"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是打电话的人。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "relative"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 family member，亲属。医生以为打电话的人可能是家属。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 308.61,
      "end": 314.226,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后一秒反转："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'No,' the patient answered, 'I am Mr. John Gilbert.'"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 314.576,
      "end": 325.296,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他听起来像 caller asking about a patient；其实 he was the patient。这个故事的 punchline 就落在 patient 和 caller 的身份重合上。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 325.646,
      "end": 328.166,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课最容易误会的地方是什么？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 328.516,
      "end": 331.497,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "以为 John 在教我们怎么绕过医生？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 331.847,
      "end": 344.487,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对，所以要先说清楚：这是旧时代电话场景里的幽默反转。今天医院通常会保护 private medical information，医生不会随便在电话里告诉别人手术结果。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 344.837,
      "end": 349.447,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "hospital exchange"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么重要？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 349.797,
      "end": 359.637,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为它解释了旧场景。John 不是直接用手机打医生微信，也不是查 app。他先打给医院总机，再让总机接 Doctor Millington。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 359.986,
      "end": 363.747,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "exchange"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "听起来像“交换”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 364.097,
      "end": 372.297,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这课里不是。它是 telephone exchange, switchboard，总机。我们可以把它想成 old phone routing desk。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 372.647,
      "end": 375.908,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么这课 indirect questions 这么多？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 376.258,
      "end": 386.058,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为整个计划都是 indirect 的。他不直接问 “Am I all right?” 而是正式地问 whether, if, when，把自己说成 another patient。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 386.408,
      "end": 390.862,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后医生问"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "relative"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是什么意思？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 391.212,
      "end": 402.684,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "relative"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 family member。医生问 caller 是不是病人的亲属，John 才揭示：不是亲属，我就是 John Gilbert。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 403.034,
      "end": 410.93,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "While John Gilbert was in hospital, he asked his doctor to tell him whether his operation had been successful, but the doctor refused to do so."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 411.28,
      "end": 415.384,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The following day, the patient asked for a bedside telephone."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 44,
      "start": 415.734,
      "end": 421.014,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "When he was alone, he telephoned the hospital exchange and asked for Doctor Millington."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 45,
      "start": 421.363,
      "end": 428.275,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "When the doctor answered the phone, Mr. Gilbert said he was inquiring about a certain patient, a Mr. John Gilbert."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 46,
      "start": 428.625,
      "end": 434.217,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He asked if Mr. Gilbert's operation had been successful and the doctor told him that it had been."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 47,
      "start": 434.567,
      "end": 441.791,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He then asked when Mr. Gilbert would be allowed to go home and the doctor told him that he would have to stay in hospital for another two weeks."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 48,
      "start": 442.141,
      "end": 446.725,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Then Dr. Millington asked the caller if he was a relative of the patient."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 49,
      "start": 447.075,
      "end": 450.987,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'No,' the patient answered, 'I am Mr. John Gilbert.'"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
